  <brief_title>Adequate Additional Bronchial Cuff Volume to Achieve Blood-tight Seal After Air-tight Seal in Double Lumen Tube</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Seoul National University Hospital</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Seoul National University Hospital</source>
  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to find the adequate additional bronchial cuff volume after
      achievement of air-tight seal, that can achieve blood-tight seal(preventing leakage of blood
      through cuff) in double lumen tube
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
